Admin
Description

The admin object provides information on the Intercom teammate. You can see more about this on the Admin Model page of our API Reference.

Example Object
{
  admin: {
    type: "admin",
    id: "814860",
    name: "IntercomTest",
    email: "theadmin@example.com",
    job_title: "Existentialist",
    away_mode_enabled: false,
    away_mode_reassign: false,
